897. J Clin Med. 2021 Jun 17;10(12):2666. doi: 10.3390/jcm10122666.

Switching to Brolucizumab in Neovascular Age-Related Macular Degeneration 
Incompletely Responsive to Ranibizumab or Aflibercept: Real-Life 6 Month 
